VALUES
  ('b9a27a6b-2947-4da0-ac98-1ea3a4b3d246','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',96.0,'owner ~70 (68+ band), +4 long-tenure 45yr',70.0,'multi-staff (18 emp) 45yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book',88.0,'7 strong coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); dated website / pre-2015 era; no CAD/CAM software named; no modern equipment / generic equipment language; no hiring/apprenticeship messaging; phone-forward / no online intake',90.0,'Metro=Houston; nudge +5 (oil+gas+petrochem buyer pool). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',86.0,'A_acquire_self','Reliable Machinists Corporation (Houston, TX) — 45yr CNC shop, owner ~70. L1=96 | L2=70 | L3=88 | L4=90 -> final=86 (A_acquire_self). Coasting tells: 7 matched. Enrichment note: Classic A-tier target profile: founder-led 45yr tenure, owner ~70, narrow oilfield niche, no diversification, dated web presence, no certs beyond API spec compliance. ''Chung and his family continue their traditions'' language suggests informal family involvement but no clear named successor. Houston Harris County.','certification uplift (ISO 9001 / AS9100) opens aerospace book and lifts margin; modernize CAD/CAM stack and add online quoting to compress quote-to-cash; diversify into aerospace/defense/medical to de-risk single-cycle exposure.','medium',0.7),
  ('e8a4c118-e753-404d-a554-38d36b6d227e','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',96.0,'owner ~70 (68+ band), +4 long-tenure 48yr',70.0,'multi-staff (22 emp) 48yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book',88.0,'5 strong coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); no CAD/CAM software named; no modern equipment / generic equipment language; tell: family-owned; tell: no certifications',90.0,'Metro=Houston; nudge +5 (oil+gas+petrochem buyer pool). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',86.0,'A_acquire_self','H&W Manufacturing (Spring, TX) — 48yr CNC shop, owner ~70. L1=96 | L2=70 | L3=88 | L4=90 -> final=86 (A_acquire_self). Coasting tells: 5 matched. Enrichment note: CLASSIC A-TIER: family-owned 48yr Spring (N Harris) shop, owns 34K sqft building (built 2009), no ISO/AS9100/ITAR cert posture (modest sophistication), Swiss screw specialist. Owner pair likely late 60s/70s. Strong successor risk and likely to consider sale.','certification uplift (ISO 9001 / AS9100) opens aerospace book and lifts margin; modernize CAD/CAM stack and add online quoting to compress quote-to-cash.','medium',0.65),
  ('15e1397c-c939-4084-8285-2c762b82fba8','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',96.0,'owner ~72 (68+ band), +4 long-tenure 47yr',70.0,'multi-staff (25 emp) 47yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book',88.0,'4 strong coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); dated website / pre-2015 era; owner-operator / founder still active; tell: no iso',88.0,'Metro=DFW; nudge +5 (Lockheed/Bell aerospace + general industrial). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',86.0,'A_acquire_self','Halsey Manufacturing (Denton, TX) — 47yr CNC shop, owner ~72. L1=96 | L2=70 | L3=88 | L4=88 -> final=86 (A_acquire_self). Coasting tells: 4 matched. Enrichment note: Top A-tier candidate. Don Halsey age + tenure + named-customer-list creates classic coasting-with-real-cash profile. Verify via TX SOS officer filings.','certification uplift (ISO 9001 / AS9100) opens aerospace book and lifts margin.','medium',0.8),
  ('8d7db575-08ee-4e42-8579-735c40aa1966','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',96.0,'owner ~68 (68+ band), +4 long-tenure 44yr',85.0,'multi-staff (30 emp) 44yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book; AS9100 +10 (aerospace premium), ISO 9001 +5',67.0,'2 coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); owner-operator / founder still active',90.0,'Metro=Houston; nudge +5 (oil+gas+petrochem buyer pool). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',84.0,'A_acquire_self','Westfield Machine, Inc. (Houston, TX) — 44yr CNC shop, owner ~68. L1=96 | L2=85 | L3=67 | L4=90 -> final=84 (A_acquire_self). Certs: ISO 9001, AS9100. Coasting tells: 2 matched. Enrichment note: TOP ETA TARGET: 44-yr family-owned tenure, ISO 9001:2015 + API Q1 + AS9100D, modern multi-brand equipment fleet (Doosan/Okuma/Toyoda etc), gas turbine niche. Owner founded 1982 = likely ~68-72 now. Site narrative emphasizes owner-direct customer model = handoff sensitivity. STRONG ETA candidate with family-successor...','diversify into aerospace/defense/medical to de-risk single-cycle exposure.','medium',0.75),
  ('a3aead49-e06f-4c22-bcf9-0cf4ad13d54c','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',86.0,'owner ~65 (63-67 band), +4 long-tenure 51yr',70.0,'multi-staff (12 emp) 51yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book',88.0,'7 strong coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); dated website / pre-2015 era; no CAD/CAM software named; phone-forward / no online intake; tell: family-owned; tell: no certifications',88.0,'Metro=DFW; nudge +5 (Lockheed/Bell aerospace + general industrial). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',83.0,'A_acquire_self','Bates Machine & Mfg., Inc. (Farmersville, TX) — 51yr CNC shop, owner ~65. L1=86 | L2=70 | L3=88 | L4=88 -> final=83 (A_acquire_self). Coasting tells: 7 matched. Enrichment note: Strong A-tier candidate. Diversified industry mix (11 industries) suggests recession-resistant book. Validate cash health via Texas Workforce employer reports or DataAxle.','certification uplift (ISO 9001 / AS9100) opens aerospace book and lifts margin; modernize CAD/CAM stack and add online quoting to compress quote-to-cash.','medium',0.78),
  ('b14b1159-e0a1-4553-be02-9d7bf5ef773c','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',96.0,'owner ~72 (68+ band), +4 long-tenure 59yr',70.0,'multi-staff (12 emp) 59yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book',88.0,'7 strong coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); no CAD/CAM software named; no modern equipment / generic equipment language; social media absent; tell: family-owned; tell: no certifications',55.0,'Metro=East Texas; nudge 0. SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',81.0,'A_acquire_self','Precision Enterprise, Inc. (Woodville, TX) — 59yr CNC shop, owner ~72. L1=96 | L2=70 | L3=88 | L4=55 -> final=81 (A_acquire_self). Coasting tells: 7 matched. Enrichment note: STRONG A-TIER: 59yr tenure, DeltaCAD (legacy software), MANUAL MACHINING still in mix, NO certifications, rural East TX, family-owned pump-repair niche. Classic coasting profile. Owner likely 70s. TOP CANDIDATE.','certification uplift (ISO 9001 / AS9100) opens aerospace book and lifts margin; modernize CAD/CAM stack and add online quoting to compress quote-to-cash.','medium',0.7),
  ('1214ab4a-a960-4b2b-a82f-905d93550291','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',86.0,'owner ~65 (63-67 band), +4 long-tenure 46yr',85.0,'multi-staff (65 emp) 46yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book; AS9100 +10 (aerospace premium), ISO 9001 +5',67.0,'2 coasting tells: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell); dated website / pre-2015 era',88.0,'Metro=DFW; nudge +5 (Lockheed/Bell aerospace + general industrial). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',80.0,'A_acquire_self','Starke Machine Co. (Fort Worth, TX) — 46yr CNC shop, owner ~65. L1=86 | L2=85 | L3=67 | L4=88 -> final=80 (A_acquire_self). Certs: ISO 9001, AS9100. Coasting tells: 2 matched. Enrichment note: Solid B+ candidate. ZoomInfo revenue figure puts it right at $10M sweet spot. Verify owner identity via Texas SOS franchise tax filings.','operational tightening + ERP/quoting digitization to drive EBITDA uplift.','medium',0.7),
